{"tid":961833,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"集思廣益 究竟聽日出唔出街","createTime":"2018-12-30T11:58:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-30T15:54:03.000Z","uid":227248,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"88e00880a39ad95e32d2ab6209bc4b961666f93f","tid":961833,"uid":227248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T11:58:48.000Z","msg":"話說小弟係毒撚一個,咁聖誕節就自己去睇戲啦,因為冇人陪冇朋友吖嘛,去到戲院同個職員講想睇水行俠,佢話兩位$180,有冇學生證?<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 然後我答佢我自己一個嚟睇,佢即刻同我講對唔住先生,然後得低頭係咁笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住睇完戲就肚餓啦,於是就是但入咗間餐廳食嘢,一入到去佢就同我講兩位?坐呢度呀! 吸收過上次嘅教訓,我決定唔咁快講,直到佢問我食咩落單嗰陣,我先同佢講我一個人,本身以為冇事啦,點知食食下有個侍應行過嚟同我講,我哋有份禮物畀你,祝你聖誕快樂呀,先生! <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如題,小弟31號應唔應該出街??<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"273a9f97dfa87b882d5c636ee18229fcc9204ea4","tid":961833,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T11:59:46.000Z","msg":"唔應該"},{"pid":"45ff7c151c6d755d89b21d342723f2b60c7c5d29","tid":961833,"uid":172844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T12:01:30.000Z","msg":"邊間餐廳一個人食就有禮物送<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3cdb70daed8b404e6ab07ff7035ad45a99cf7f9","tid":961833,"uid":227248,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"45ff7c151c6d755d89b21d342723f2b60c7c5d29","tid":961833,"uid":172844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T12:01:30.000Z","msg":"邊間餐廳一個人食就有禮物送<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T12:02:46.000Z","msg":"睇嚟大家都係巴打wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3da4829896c81ad64821646fc1505cc350015d6","tid":961833,"uid":227248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"273a9f97dfa87b882d5c636ee18229fcc9204ea4","tid":961833,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score"